law.history: Repealed 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 130, sec. 182, effective January 1, 1997. -- Amended 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 118, sec. 40, effective July 1, 1987. -- Created 1958 Ky. Acts ch. 77, sec. 8-316, effective July 1, 1960.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Purchaser's right to requisites for registration of transfer, pledge or release on books.
